flowchart LR
    U[User]
    UI[Chat UI\nStreamlit or Web App]
    Router[Request Router\nSQL vs RAG vs Hybrid]
    Orchestrator[Hybrid Agent Orchestrator]
    Answer[Answer Composer\nCitations and Grounding]

    subgraph Retrieval[SharePoint RAG Path]
        SPTool[SharePoint Connector]
        Extract[Document Extraction\nPDF DOCX PPTX XLSX MD]
        Chunk[Chunking and Metadata]
        Index[Vector or Hybrid Index]
        Retrieve[Retriever\nSemantic + Keyword + Filters]
    end

    subgraph Data[SQL Path]
        Guard[SQL Guardrails\nAllowlist + Validation]
        SQLTool[SQL Tool]
        Fabric[(SQL Database / Fabric)]
    end

    subgraph Model[LLM Layer]
        LLM[Azure OpenAI / LLM]
    end

    subgraph Actions[Optional Action Tools]
        Mail[Email Tool]
        Export[Export Tool]
        Alert[Workflow / Alert Tool]
    end

    U --> UI
    UI --> Router
    Router --> Orchestrator

    Orchestrator -->|RAG| Retrieve
    SPTool --> Extract --> Chunk --> Index --> Retrieve

    Orchestrator -->|SQL| Guard --> SQLTool --> Fabric
    Fabric --> SQLTool --> Orchestrator

    Retrieve --> Orchestrator
    Orchestrator --> LLM
    LLM --> Answer
    Answer --> UI

    Orchestrator --> Mail
    Orchestrator --> Export
    Orchestrator --> Alert